        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Kids and Family</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Join our life-changing sessions designed to strengthen family bonds and enhance the well-being of children and adults alike.</p>
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 text-dark-brown-bg justify-between">
          <a href="#" class="font-semibold hover:underline text-brown-text">Read More</a>
          <i class="fa fa-arrow-right p-1 text-white bg-dark-brown-bg rounded-full mr-2" aria-hidden="true"></i>
