<div class="practice flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-stretch justify-center pb-24 px-4 pt-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 pt-12 relative bg-cover bg-center w-full">
  <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-opacity-75 z-0"></div>
  
  <div class="relative z-10 left w-full lg:w-1/2 p-4 flex flex-col justify-center">
    <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 mb-4">
      <span class="w-2 h-2 bg-dark-brown-bg rounded-full"></span>
      <span class="w-1/12 h-px bg-dark-brown-bg"></span>
      <span class="uppercase tracking-widest font-mulish text-brown-text">Frequently Asked Questions</span>
    </div>
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Have questions? Get in touch or look at the FAQ section.</h2>
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl mb-6">Find answers to common questions about our services, policies, and more. If you have any other queries, feel free to get in touch with us directly.</p>
    <p>Have more questions in mind? <a href="#" class=" text-brown-text underline">Get In Touch</a> with me.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="relative z-10 right w-full lg:w-1/2 p-4 flex flex-col space-y-4 mt-8 lg:mt-0">
    <div class="faq-section flex flex-col divide-y divide-gray-300">
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">What services do you offer?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>We offer a range of psychological services including individual therapy, couples counseling, family therapy, and group therapy. Our services are designed to support mental health and well-being for individuals of all ages.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">How do I book an appointment?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>You can book an appointment by calling our office at 0788345647 or by visiting our website and using the online booking system. We will confirm your appointment via email or phone.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">What can I expect during my first session?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>During your first session, we will discuss your reasons for seeking therapy and gather some background information. This will help us understand your needs and work with you to develop a treatment plan.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">Do you offer online therapy?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>Yes, we offer online therapy sessions for clients who prefer or require remote services. Online therapy provides the same level of care as in-person sessions and can be conducted via video call.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">How confidential is my therapy?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>Your confidentiality is of utmost importance to us. All sessions and records are kept confidential, and we adhere to strict privacy policies. Exceptions to confidentiality occur only in situations where there is a risk of harm to yourself or others.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">What are your fees?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>Our fees vary depending on the type and length of service. Please contact our office at 0788345647 or visit our website for detailed information on our fee structure and any available sliding scale options.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
      <details class="py-2">
        <summary class="cursor-pointer text-brown-text text-lg font-semibold focus:underline">How can I contact you for more information?</summary>
        <div class="px-4 pb-4 text-gray-600">
          <p>If you have any questions or need more information, please feel free to contact us at 0788345647 or email us at <a href="mailto:example@gmail.com" class="underline">info@unburden.com</a>. We are here to help and support you.</p>
        </div>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>